{"calories":"720","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"Near our offices in New York City, it seems like there’s a poke bowl offered at every restaurant we visit. After some, ahem, significant research, we were inspired to create a vegetarian version showcasing one of our go-to fall ingredients: sweet potato. Hearty brown rice is seasoned with Japanese spice mix \u003ci\u003efurikake\u003c/i\u003e then topped with sesame-roasted sweet potatoes, tangy cucumbers and scallions, and seaweed salad. Oh, and there’s creamy Sriracha mayo \u003ci\u003eand\u003c/i\u003e creamy sliced avocado, because, obviously. ","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"a2ea05239a","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/hero_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/menu_small_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/small_square_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/medium_square_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14245/recipe_profile_page_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0102.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14247/1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0109.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14247/menu_small_1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0109.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/14246/1695_Roasted_Sweet_Potato_Poke_Bowl_with_Avocado_and_Sriracha_Mayo_0106.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Roasted Sweet Potato Poke Bowl with Avocado and Sriracha Mayo","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"40-50","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"roasted-sweet-potato-poke-bowl-with-avocado-and-sriracha-mayo","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/8813/recipe_card20161003-3-qj8kez.pdf","recipe_id":1695,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Roasted Sweet Potato Poke Bowl","subtitle":"with Avocado and Sriracha Mayo","title":"Roasted Sweet Potato Poke Bowl","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did! \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eBrown rice hack: The amount of water isn’t indicated because you’ll drain the rice like you do with pasta when it's finished cooking.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eFurikake has a strong flavor. Taste it first, then decide how much you want to use. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","aluminum foil","baking sheet"],"id":1695,"ingredients":["garlic","Persian cucumber","scallion","sweet potato","brown rice","sesame seeds","furikake seasoning","gluten-free soy sauce","mayonnaise","Sriracha","avocado","seaweed salad"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"Persian cucumber","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1112/medium_square_medium_square_cucumber.jpg"},{"name":"scallion","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/53/medium_square_SCALLIONS_-4463_copy.jpg"},{"name":"sweet potato","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1272/medium_square_medium_square_sweet-potato-2.jpg"},{"name":"brown rice","quantity":"0.75","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/217/medium_square_BROWN_RICE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"sesame seeds","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/55/medium_square_sesame-seed-test.jpg"},{"name":"furikake seasoning","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1346/medium_square_furikake.jpg"},{"name":"gluten-free soy sauce","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1361/medium_square_medium_square_soy-sauce-test.jpg"},{"name":"mayonnaise","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1487/medium_square_sir_kensingtons.jpg"},{"name":"Sriracha","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/440/medium_square_SRIRACHA_copy.jpg"},{"name":"avocado","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/52/medium_square_avocado-halved1.jpg"},{"name":"seaweed salad","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1347/medium_square_seaweed_Salad.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["canola oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"canola oil","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13314/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. Rinse all produce. Halve \u003cstrong\u003ecucumber \u003c/strong\u003elengthwise and thinly slice crosswise. Trim and discard roots of \u003cstrong\u003escallions \u003c/strong\u003eand thinly slice. Cut \u003cstrong\u003esweet potatoes\u003c/strong\u003e into .5-inch dice.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Rice","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13316/recipe_card_size_3._Cook_Rice.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile sweet potatoes roast, season pot of boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003erice\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until tender, 22-25 minutes (see Recipe Tip). Drain, then sprinkle up to \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of furikake\u003c/strong\u003e over top (see Recipe Tip). Set aside.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast Sweet Potatoes","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13315/recipe_card_size_2._Roast_Potatoes.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eIn a large bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon canola oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003esesame seeds\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. \u0026nbsp;Add \u003cstrong\u003esweet potatoes \u003c/strong\u003eto bowl and toss to coat. On a foil-lined baking sheet, arrange \u003cstrong\u003esweet potatoes\u003c/strong\u003e in an even layer. Transfer to oven and roast, flipping halfway, until tender and slightly charred, about 15 minutes total.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Marinate Veggies and Make Sriracha Mayo","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13317/recipe_card_size_4._Make_Sauces.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile potatoes and rice cook, wipe bowl from sweet potatoes clean, add \u003cstrong\u003esoy sauce\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic \u003c/strong\u003eand stir to combine. Add \u003cstrong\u003ecucumber\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003escallions\u003c/strong\u003e to bowl and toss to coat. Set aside. In a small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003emayonnaise\u003c/strong\u003e and as much \u003cstrong\u003eSriracha\u003c/strong\u003e as desired (it's spicy!) until fully combined. Set aside for serving.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Prepare Avocado","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13318/recipe_card_size_5._Prepare_Avocado.jpg","description":"Halve \u003cb\u003eavocado\u003c/b\u003e and discard pit. Using a spoon, carefully scoop out flesh, discarding skin. Thinly slice.\n"},{"title":"Plate Sweet Potato Poke ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13319/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Poke.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide\u003cstrong\u003e rice \u003c/strong\u003ebetween 2 bowls and top with \u003cstrong\u003esweet potatoes\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e cucumbers and scallion\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eavocado\u003c/strong\u003e. Spoon \u003cstrong\u003eseaweed salad \u003c/strong\u003eon top and drizzle over \u003cstrong\u003eSriracha mayo\u003c/strong\u003e. Sprinkle as much \u003cstrong\u003eremaining furikake\u003c/strong\u003e as desired on top and dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Soy","slug":"soy","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}